snippet.title: Indians And Diwali | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys 
A Very Happy Diwali !!!

Special Thanks to Tanishq

As the Title is Indians And Diwali this Video has everything that happens during Diwali Festival . The most relatable and Funny Diwali Video . Scenarios like what happens on Indian families doing Diwali shopping for dhanteras shopping new utensils or jewellery shopping of gold coin , silver coin from brand like Tanishq . Kaamwali and her struggles with house cleaning waiting for diwali gifts , diwali bonus . Daughter painting diya and mom hanging diwali lights . Girls dressing up in traditional dieting whole month to look good and clicking pictures and making videos . Prepations for office diwali pooja , sisters cleaning house and competing and having fun , next day of diwali and taking off the lights , flower garlands , rangoli , giving diwali to staff , guards , kaamwali bai , Aunties for shopping for diwali pooja kheel patashe , patisha , paan , supari , sweets , favourite mathai moti choor ladoo , kaju ki barfi , bondi ke laddoo , cham cham , diwali decoration , bhandan var , diya , lights , candles , rangoli , diwali gifts dry fruits , gift box . Indian Aunties bargaining with shopkeeper , shops making huge profits during diwali dhamaka sales , going out to relatives to wish happy diwali and dealing with diwali 2023 traffic jams , giving gifts to relatives and travelling in car , indian sweets shops fully loaded with customers , eating in restaurants after diwali shopping eating dosa , chowmein , tuition mam helps kids prepare their diwali poem , diwali essay , teaching why diwali is celebrated , diwali school function costumes , diwali is the festival food , every foodie loves puri , aloo , kheer , halwa , muli ki bhujji , raita , achar , panchamrit , laxmi ganesh pooja , talking about the ban on fire crackers , diwali away from home , pg wali diwali , showing of chandi , golf gifts , buying air purifier cause of the air pollution and noise pullution caused by crackers in delhi , south delhi posh diwali partiers playing poker , drinking , tambola , diwali vlogs , diwali outfits , lehenga , suits , saree , kurti , kurta , and looking beautiful and clicking pictures . West Delhi people mocking south delhi on dieting on diwali doing keto , intermittent fasting or just drinking alchol , many more fun things covered in the diwali video .
This video is filled with Festive season memories and situations we all have been in . 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories of Diwali festival
Do share it with your friends and family , Relatives , Neighbour . A very happy diwali 2023 season to all of you and Happy deepawali  .. Comment down your Fav Part , 
Like , Share and 
Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon

Special Thanks Tanishq

Contact : 081302 08877
Map : https://goo.gl/maps/VU8CSgepaJA3iAjy5

snippet.description:

Diwali Mela starts in Gokuldham society. Everyone is super excited to buy festival lights, lamps, colors, and decorative items from the stalls. Bhide first inaugurates the beginning of the Mela by cutting the ribbon. Watch the full episode to know more.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

#tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah

snippet.title: छोटी सी सुंदर दिवाली की नई रंगोली | Diwali Beautiful Rangoli Design | Latest New Diwali Rangoli 2023
snippet.description:
On Our This Perfect Art Plus You Tube Channel You Can find Latest and Beautiful and Colourful Easy Rangoli Designs for your sweet home door Diwali Festival Decorations.

As we have know about Rangoli Designs are started many centuries ago. Some references of Rangoli Designs are also available in our scriptures. The art of rangoli has changed and rechanged over many centuries in our India. As we Know Rangoli have various names in many parts of India. In Tamil Nadu it's known as Kolam Rangoli, in Andhra it's known as muggulu Rangoli, in Karnataka it's known as muggitu Rangoli and  in Rajasthan Rangoli known as a mandana Rngoli and so on. In This Video We have a Beautiful and very Simple Rangoli Designs and Very easy indian rangoli designs for beginners, fresher's, Learner or house wife. They can easily draw these beautiful and very easy and simple rangoli designs at own home in short time and very fast for home decoration. If you enter any Hindu house in India, you are bound to be welcomed by a rangoli design which is normally drawn with chalk powder or lime stone powder or beautiful rangoli colours on the floor on this Diwali Festival. 

Latest Beautiful Rangoli Desgns and Ideas.  No matter how big or small your house is, it is always possible to create a beautiful rangoli to bring in the festivities. Let these colourful Rangoli designs for your beautiful home decorations on Sweet and Beautiful Diwali Festival 2023.

Generally Easy rangoli designs are used in almost all kinds of hindu religious occasions, festivals, weddings and many more season in our India.It's believed that rangolis ward off evil spirits from homes. So try out that beautiful and Very nice and Easy and Simple Rangoli Designs today at your home impress your all familly members and your coming guest on This Dwail Festival. 
Give your home decor a festive touch by making a beautiful rangoli design using Rangoli colours. 

Follow our Latest Rangoli making tutorial and make your colourful and beautiful rangoli designs at your Home on Our Bif Diwali Festival.

Please Like Share Our This Rangoli Designs Video... And Subscribe our Perfect Art Plus You Tube Channel...

snippet.description:

Mannat Murad Episode 14 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 13th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

snippet.title: India vs Netherlands: ఇండియా 9 మందిని బౌలింగ్‌కు దించడం వెనుక ద్రవిడ్, రోహిత్ ప్లానేంటి? BBC Telugu
snippet.description:
ఆదివారం నెదర్లాండ్స్‌తో జరిగిన ఆఖరి లీగ్ మ్యాచ్‌లో భారత బౌలింగ్‌లో ఈ టోర్నీలో ఇప్పటివరకు కనిపించని ప్రత్యేకత కనిపించింది. ఏకంగా తొమ్మిది మంది భారత ఆటగాళ్లు బౌలింగ్ చేశారు. అది కూడా స్పెషలిస్టు బౌలర్లకు పూర్తి కోటా ఇవ్వకుండానే. అయితే కెప్టెన్ రోహిత్​ శర్మ అలా ఎందుకు చేశాడు?
#TeamIndia #IndvsNed #Netherlands #RohitSharma #ViratKohli #Bowling
___________
ఫేస్‌బుక్, ఇన్‌స్టాగ్రామ్, ట్విటర్‌లలో బీబీసీ తెలుగును ఫాలో అవ్వండి.

te.title: India vs Netherlands: ఇండియా 9 మందిని బౌలింగ్‌కు దించడం వెనుక ద్రవిడ్, రోహిత్ ప్లానేంటి? BBC Telugu
te.description:
ఆదివారం నెదర్లాండ్స్‌తో జరిగిన ఆఖరి లీగ్ మ్యాచ్‌లో భారత బౌలింగ్‌లో ఈ టోర్నీలో ఇప్పటివరకు కనిపించని ప్రత్యేకత కనిపించింది. ఏకంగా తొమ్మిది మంది భారత ఆటగాళ్లు బౌలింగ్ చేశారు. అది కూడా స్పెషలిస్టు బౌలర్లకు పూర్తి కోటా ఇవ్వకుండానే. అయితే కెప్టెన్ రోహిత్​ శర్మ అలా ఎందుకు చేశాడు?
#TeamIndia #IndvsNed #Netherlands #RohitSharma #ViratKohli #Bowling
___________
ఫేస్‌బుక్, ఇన్‌స్టాగ్రామ్, ట్విటర్‌లలో బీబీసీ తెలుగును ఫాలో అవ్వండి.

ఇన్‌స్టాగ్రామ్: https://www.instagram.com/bbcnewstelugu/

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3927 | 13 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3927: Diwali Ki Tayariyan
--------------------------------------------------------
When Sodhi discovers that Bhide has forgotten the Suvichaar, he tries to pull an innocent prank on him. He gives Abdul the order to keep hidden Bhide's whiteboard, on which he writes the daily thinking quotation. When Bhide notices the board is missing, he becomes suspicious. Dr. Hathi calms Bhide down as he begins to panic. Bhide informs Sodhi that his board, which he has called "Sakhanand," is his second favorite item, after his scooter, "Sakharam." Will Sodhi reveal his trick to Bhide and inform him about it? What reaction will Bhide give to it?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3927, 13 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.description:

എല്ലാ നാട്ടിലും ഉണ്ടാവും സ്വന്തം വീട്ടിലെ കാര്യത്തെക്കാൾ അടുത്ത വീട്ടിലെ കാര്യങ്ങൾ അറിയാൻ ആകാംക്ഷ കൂടുതൽ ഉള്ള ആളുകൾ 🤣.. എന്ത് ചെയ്യാം അവരൊക്കെ ജീവിതത്തിന്റെ നല്ല കാലം മുഴുവൻ ജീവിതം ആസ്വദിക്കാൻ കഴിക്കാതെ പോയ ആളുകൾ ആണ്. ഇപ്പോഴത്തെ ആളുകൾ അവരുടെ ജീവിതം ആസ്വദിക്കുന്നത് കാണുമ്പോൾ അവർക്കു അല്പം കുശുമ്പ് തോന്നുന്നത് സ്വാഭാവികം 😁..... video ഇഷ്ടമായാൽ subscribe ചെയ്യാൻ മറക്കരുത് ട്ടോ.. പിന്നെ e video എടുത്ത് ആരും വേറെ കൊണ്ട് പോയി upload ചെയ്യുകയും അരുത് 😍... ഇത്രയും വായിച്ചതിൽ സന്തോഷം 💖

snippet.title: Maa Bina Diwali | Sahaparivar | EP-03 | A Family Mockumentary Drama | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Step into the uproarious world of the "Sahaparivar" as we bring you a sidesplitting comedy sketch that gives a mockumentary-style peek into the charming chaos of a typical Sunday morning.
In this episode we begin with the disappearance of the mother 'Shilpa' and start to progress into the chaotic journey where the family hides the fact of shilpa's disappearance from their neighbors. But at the heart of all of this, a question still remains - Where is Shilpa? Stay till the end of the episode to find out.

snippet.title: ₹1,00,000 RC Car Race Challenge in Mini City Ft. Crazy XYZ🔥 - कौनसी गाड़ी जीतेगी रेस?
snippet.description:
🏎️ Buckle up for the ultimate thrill ride as Unacademy Spotlight brings you the most exciting ₹1,00,000 RC Car Race Challenge! 🏁

In this adrenaline-fueled race, Unacademy Centre students compete for cash prizes totaling 1 Lakh rupees. But here's the twist—it's not just any race; it's a high-stakes competition set in a meticulously crafted Mini City, spanning from our Unacademy Centre in Delhi to the one in Jaipur!

The race kicks off at our Unacademy Centre in Delhi, navigating through challenging terrains, conquering obstacles, and zipping through specially designed tracks. The destination? Our Unacademy Centre in Jaipur—a journey filled with twists, turns, and nail-biting moments!

The stakes are high, with a whopping ₹1,00,000 in cash prizes up for grabs! Who will emerge as the RC Car Race Champion and claim the lion's share of the prize money?

At Unacademy, we believe in the spirit of learning, challenging, and pushing boundaries. This RC Car Race Challenge embodies our commitment to fostering a culture of fun, excitement, and friendly competition among students.
If you're interested to know more and check out the Unacademy Centre for IIT JEE, NEET UG and Foundation near you. Click here - https://mrkt.unacademy.com/video-centres

So hit that like button, share the excitement, and subscribe to Unacademy Spotlight for more unique challenges and engaging content!

#RCCarRace #MiniCityChallenge #UnacademySpotlightChallenge #RCRaceMadness

snippet.title: "കരച്ചിൽ കാണാൻ ഇനി ആരും വരേണ്ട"| Renu Sudhi | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
#joshtalksmalayalam #kollamsudhi #flowersstarmagic 

"വിധി ചിലപ്പോഴൊക്കെ ക്രൂരമാണ്".. ഇങ്ങനൊരു അനുഭവത്തിലൂടെ കടന്നുപോയതാണ് രേണു സുധി. രേണുവിന്റെ ഇപ്പോഴുള്ള ജീവിതം നിങ്ങൾ കേൾക്കേണ്ടതാണ്. ഇത്തരം പ്രതിസന്ധിഘട്ടത്തിൽ എങ്ങനെയാണ് രേണുവും, ആ കുടുംബവും ജീവിച്ചു കാണിച്ചുതരുന്നതെന്ന് കേൾക്കാം. ടോക്ക് കാണാം.

Kollam Sudhi was a beloved comedian in the Malayalam entertainment industry who left a lasting impact on his audiences. In this emotional talk, his wife Renu Sudhi speaks candidly about her life with Kollam Sudhi, sharing heartwarming anecdotes and memories. She also touches on the challenges they faced as a family and how they overcame them together. This powerful and touching talk is a tribute to the legacy of Kollam Sudhi, and a must-watch for anyone who loved him. Join us as we celebrate the life and work of this remarkable artist.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.

You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayali's. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവയെ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഒരു സമ്മേളനമായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

localized.title: "കരച്ചിൽ കാണാൻ ഇനി ആരും വരേണ്ട"| Renu Sudhi | Josh Talks Malayalam
localized.description:
#joshtalksmalayalam #kollamsudhi #flowersstarmagic 

"വിധി ചിലപ്പോഴൊക്കെ ക്രൂരമാണ്".. ഇങ്ങനൊരു അനുഭവത്തിലൂടെ കടന്നുപോയതാണ് രേണു സുധി. രേണുവിന്റെ ഇപ്പോഴുള്ള ജീവിതം നിങ്ങൾ കേൾക്കേണ്ടതാണ്. ഇത്തരം പ്രതിസന്ധിഘട്ടത്തിൽ എങ്ങനെയാണ് രേണുവും, ആ കുടുംബവും ജീവിച്ചു കാണിച്ചുതരുന്നതെന്ന് കേൾക്കാം. ടോക്ക് കാണാം.

Kollam Sudhi was a beloved comedian in the Malayalam entertainment industry who left a lasting impact on his audiences. In this emotional talk, his wife Renu Sudhi speaks candidly about her life with Kollam Sudhi, sharing heartwarming anecdotes and memories. She also touches on the challenges they faced as a family and how they overcame them together. This powerful and touching talk is a tribute to the legacy of Kollam Sudhi, and a must-watch for anyone who loved him. Join us as we celebrate the life and work of this remarkable artist.

माँ गंगा | Episode 01

Ganga is one of the most sacred rivers in India. 
People call Ganga, Maiyaa & Maa..but how does a river turns into a mother? We shall find out. 

==========================================================

What is Melodies of India? 

Magic Monkey, a new age travel YouTube channel travelled and explored by Raunaq Sahni is thrilled to announce an extraordinary and ambitious project. In the quest to unravel the soul of India, Raunaq embarks on a six-month odyssey across the country, meticulously documenting the essence of what it truly means to be Indian. 

The "Melodies of India" project as envisioned by Raunaq is an expedition that aims to capture the heart and spirit of India, transcending its deep-rooted cultures into a visually captivating series of photographs and videos, each narrating a unique facet of our incredible nation. These photographs and videos will serve as visual testimonies, encapsulating the diversity, traditions, and modernisation of India. 

He will later publish 11 photographs along with the moving stories in a Photobook.

snippet.title: Navratri Ke Liya Budget Nahi Hai | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Full Episode 3909 | 23 Oct 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3909: Navratri Ke Liya Budget Nahi Hai
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide has wrapped himself with a blanket to avoid spilling food or tea since he is wearing a new kurta to fulfill an order. Madhavi is eager to see his new kurta, but Bhide is apprehensive about showing it off. Madhavi becomes agitated and tries to pull a trick on him with his tea. Bhide eventually removes the cover, and Madhavi is surprised by his appearance. Popatlal received a massive steel container from the marriage after finishing his ten-year membership, but he is unable to open it. All of the Gokuldham men try and fail to unlock it. What's inside the container?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episode No - 3909
Produced By - Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:  https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi

This Diwali enjoy your favorite Kapil Sharma Show with your loved ones. Grab a box of sweets and celebrate Deepavali with your favorite characters from the show. Kapil is here to entertain you with his hilarious jokes and mind-blowing humor. Keep watching and stay tuned for more entertaining episodes!

Show Name: The Kapil Sharma Show 
Producers: Kapil Sharma, Salman Khan, Deepak Dhar
Guests: Salim-Sulaiman, Yohani, Sukhwinder Singh, Mame Khan, Devi Sri Prasad, and Akriti Kakar

#latestcomedy #comedy2023 #kapilsharma #thekapilsharmashow #sonyliv #comedy #thekapilsharmashowfullepisodes #दीकपिलशर्माशो 

About The Kapil Sharma Show : 
----------------------------------------------------------------
Kapil Sharma is back with a new 'Salah Center' (Consultancy Business) in a Mohollah with absurd characters. The wealthy milkman Bachcha Yadav (Kiku Sharda) with his wife Titli Yadav (Bharti Singh) and sister-in-law Bhoori (Sumona Singh) is the one who has rented out houses within the Mohollah and is Kapil Sharma's business partner. The neighbors in the Mohollah are also full of quirks and don't shy away from the antics. With celebrities gracing every episode, The Kapil Sharma Show promises fun-filled entertaining weekends.

Click here to watch the clips of The Kapil Sharma Show- Diwali Special:

snippet.title: Gulab Jamun with Instant Gulab Jamun Mix Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make gulab jamun recipe in tamil. This gulab jamun is made with instant jamun mix. This is very easy to make only requires milk and sugar. The gulab jamun mix can be used in place of mava / khoya. We can use coconut flakes and other nuts to decorate and add texture to these spongy gulab jamuns.
#gulabjamun #gulabjamunrecipe #gulabjamunwithmix 

Friends, please do try this gulab jamun recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Spread the joy cooking during this festival season. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking. 

Wishing everyone a very happy Diwali and enjoy this festival season with homemade sweets.

175g Instant Gulab Jamun mix (1.5 cup)
1/2 cup Milk approx
3 cup Sugar
3 cup Water
few Saffron
Cardamom powder
1/2 tsp Ghee

snippet.title: Maa Nahi Saas Hoon Main Episode 11 - [Eng Sub] - Hammad Shoaib - Sumbul Iqbal - 13th November 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Maa Nahi Saas Hoon Main Episode 11 - [Eng Sub] - Hammad Shoaib - Sumbul Iqbal - Farhan Ally Agha - 13th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

This story revolves around Mehreen and her daughter Areej, who was born after years of prayers. Prior to her birth, Mehreen and her husband had been caring for Salman, Areej's cousin. However, a tragedy struck, separating Areej from her family. Afterwards, Mehreen decided to raise Salman as her own son.
Years later, Salman crosses paths with Urooj, a beautiful and fearless girl, the daughter of school teacher Shoaib and his wife Naseem. Initially resistant to Salman's advances, Urooj eventually falls in love with him. Unbeknownst to Salman and his family, Urooj is none other than Areej, Mehreen's long-lost daughter.
Will Urooj discover the truth about her identity? How will the family come to know that Urooj is Mehreen’s long-lost daughter, Areej? How will Urooj react when she gets to know that Mehreen is her real mother? What impact will Urooj’s identity have on Salman? Will Mehreen accept Urooj as her daughter? Will Urooj’s true identity pose a threat to her relationship with Salman?

snippet.title: Diwali Special Access: Takeshi’s Castle - Episode 1 | @BBKiVines  | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
With joy and laughter, this festive season we are presenting the first episode of Takeshi’s Castle dubbed in Hindi by Bhuvan Bam. Relive your childhood memories with the classic games and new terrifying obstacles. Watch all episodes available only on Prime Video India.

Watch Now - https://bit.ly/TakeshisCastleOnPrime

About:
Bhuvan Bam lends his distinctive voice and unique humor as commentator in the brand-new season of Takeshi's Castle. Classic games are making a comeback with new and terrifying obstacles emerging one after another. The lord of the castle, Beat Takeshi, entrusts Bananaman to protect it. Subaru Kimura is the attack force’s new leader. The elite team gathers to bring down the revived Takeshi’s Castle.

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

snippet.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Always remember who you are…

The four nations of the world once lived in harmony, with the Avatar, master of all four elements, keeping peace between them. But everything changed when the Fire Nation attacked and wiped out the Air Nomads, the first step taken by the firebenders towards conquering the world.

AVATAR: THE LAST AIRBENDER, follows a young Air Nomad named Aang, as he reawakens to a world ravaged by war. Together with his newfound friends Sokka and Katara, he embarks on an action-packed quest to take his rightful place as the next AVATAR.

This new live-action reimagining of the award-winning Nickelodeon animated series comes to Netflix in 2024.

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 247 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Baylagaam Episode 37 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 13th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

Written By: Huma Hina Nafees
Directed By: Zahid Mehmood
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3926 | 11 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3926: Jethalal's Surprise Gift
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha is relieved to learn that his best friend, Taarak, has already planned a gift for Babita. Jetha is intrigued by the large, wrapped package and inquires of Taarak about the gift. Jetha eventually comes with the present to Iyer and Babita's place. Babita is surprised to see a black box as she opens the present. When Jetha phones Taarak to inquire about the present, Taarak informs him about a switch hidden under the box. So, what exactly is the gift? Will Babita be pleased? Will she become agitated?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3926, 11 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता आरती | Om Jai Laxmi Mata Aarti | Diwali Aarti | Laxmi Mata Aarti | Alka Yagnik
snippet.description:
Tips Bhakti Prem Presets Diwali 2023 Special Popular Lakshmi Aarti "ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता | Om Jai Laxmi Mata " Sung By Alka Yagnik. on @tipsbhaktiprem  

#diwalispecial #omjailaxmimata #lakshmiaarti #diwali2023

To receive regular updates on devotional songs subscribe to us on the following link: https://www.youtube.com/BhaktiPrem

Song Credits:
Singer(s): Alka Yagnik
Music Director: Sayed Ali
Lyricist: Traditional

Importance of Laxmi Mata : 
Goddess Lakshmi is the Hindu goddess of wealth, fortune and prosperity (both material and spiritual). Her name is derived from the Sanskrit word ‘Lakshya’, which means aim or goal. 
She is the wife and Shakti (energy) of Vishnu, one of the principal deities of Hinduism and the Supreme Being in the Vaishnavism Tradition. Lakshmi is also an important deity in Jainism as well as Buddhism. 

Lakshmi is also called 'Sri' or 'Thirumagal' because she is endowed with six auspicious and divine qualities, or gunas, and is the divine strength of Vishnu. 

Lakshmi is depicted in Indian art as an elegantly dressed, prosperity-showering golden-coloured woman with an owl as her vehicle, signifying the importance of economic activity in the maintenance of life, her ability to move, work and prevail in confusing darkness. 

She is often depicted as part of the Trinity (Tridevi) consisting of Saraswati, Lakshmi and Parvati.
The festivals of Diwali and Sharad Purnima (Kojagiri Purnima) are celebrated in her honour.

Benefits of Performing Maa Lakshmi Aarti :

Lakshmi Aarti is majorly done on Diwali, office/ house-warmings to take the blessings of the goddess of Wealth, Luxury and Prosperity. The Hindu culture strongly believes that Goddess Lakshmi Provides one with financial wellbeing and material gains.

Importance of Laxmi Mata : 
Goddess Lakshmi is the Hindu goddess of wealth, fortune and prosperity (both material and spiritual). Her name is derived from the Sanskrit word ‘Lakshya’, which means aim or goal. 
She is the wife and Shakti (energy) of Vishnu, one of the principal deities of Hinduism and the Supreme Being in the Vaishnavism Tradition. Lakshmi is also an important deity in Jainism as well as Buddhism. 

Lakshmi is also called 'Sri' or 'Thirumagal' because she is endowed with six auspicious and divine qualities, or gunas, and is the divine strength of Vishnu. 

Lakshmi is depicted in Indian art as an elegantly dressed, prosperity-showering golden-coloured woman with an owl as her vehicle, signifying the importance of economic activity in the maintenance of life, her ability to move, work and prevail in confusing darkness. 

She is often depicted as part of the Trinity (Tridevi) consisting of Saraswati, Lakshmi and Parvati.
The festivals of Diwali and Sharad Purnima (Kojagiri Purnima) are celebrated in her honour.

Benefits of Performing Maa Lakshmi Aarti :

Lakshmi Aarti is majorly done on Diwali, office/ house-warmings to take the blessings of the goddess of Wealth, Luxury and Prosperity. The Hindu culture strongly believes that Goddess Lakshmi Provides one with financial wellbeing and material gains.

Ye kahaani hai gaanv ki seedhi saadi Lajo ki. Kuchh paristhitiyon ke kaaran Lajo ki shaadi ho jaati hai sheher ke modern laddke Nikhil se. Wahin doosri taraf Nikhil, Ishana se pyaar karta hai. Lajo apne rishte ko nibhaane ki poori koshish karti hai, lekin aakhirkaar wo faisla leti hai Nikhil ko uske pyaar se milaane ka. Ab kya karega Nikhil? Kya wo Ishana se shaadi kar lega, ya Lajo ko apnaayega? Jaanne ke liye dekhiye 'Gustakh Dil'.
